# For details of the following setting, see
# https://vxlabs.com/2021/03/21/mbsync-copyarrivaldate-yes/
CopyArrivalDate yes

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User david.a.porter@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/Mail/gmail.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
Expunge Both
